ðŸ¦– Dino Run

A state-machine-based game implemented in SystemVerilog and deployed on the Basys3 FPGA Board. 
The game mimics the classic Dino Run where the player controls a dinosaur to jump or duck obstacles.

ðŸŽ¯ Goals
